Package: org.grails.datastore.mapping.simpledb.model.types

[Java] Class SimpleDBTypeConverterRegistrar

      • org.grails.datastore.mapping.simpledb.model.types.SimpleDBTypeConverterRegistrar

      • A registrar that registers type converters used for SimpleDB. For example, numeric types are padded with zeros because AWS SimpleDB stores everything as a string and without padding ordering of numerics would not work.

        Authors:
        Roman Stepanenko
        Since:
        0.1
